ee58afd2","tid":183651,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:53:01.000Z","msg":"之前買左<br />\nAllianz US High Yield<br />\nAllianz Asia Flexi Bind<br />\n<br />\n而家諗住買<br />\nTempleton Global Total Return 同<br />\nAB FCP - Global High Yield Portfolio <br />\n呢兩隻各路高手點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c50b6f1e8d622f66f863ef48eeef28e245de45d","tid":183651,"uid":67115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:54:48.000Z","msg":"100萬入門 創業版<br />\n保證派8%息一年 一年期<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb5b242498f9329b5252e1eee992ddb98852941","tid":183651,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:54:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同問<br />\n平時買開股票<br />\n想問下有無年息3-5% bond推介<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小心賺息輸價<br />\n要留意派息有幾多%係由本金攞出來</blockquote><br />\n我對bond無乜認識<br />\n有無邊種bond係到期一定收到定額息而唔會影響到本金？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大把bond有monthly cash distribution<br />\n可以去 FSM 到望下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed7c5ca83f82d8a50b6c3c61ddf4ebc948b00ab","tid":183651,"uid":67115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:55:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>100萬入門 創業版<br />\n保證派8%息一年 一年期<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">債券</span>"},{"pid":"72046cb508610f739f4edb7476e9f760ec9b76be","tid":183651,"uid":70008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:01:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩 bond fund 推介<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔建議你買bond funds, <br />\n<br />\n1) bond funds 嘅回報好取決於利率。 利率升嘅時候，bond嘅價值會下跌。由於而家係喺利息上升嘅週期， 所以如無意外你都會輸錢。<br />\n<br />\n2) 如果你買funds嘅話，每年淨係手續費都收你1.x%。<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢真係有啲好處，譬如佢可以令你買到一啲平時買唔到ge bonds (譬如一啲入場費要 USD 1M ge bonds) 又或者 diversification effect。 總體嚟講我都唔建議你買。<br />\n<br />\n不過都係嗰句，錢係你嘅，你鍾意點玩就點玩"},{"pid":"749d02a070814fec3391c01222eac29c5fc70ca9","tid":183651,"uid":70008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:15:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同問<br />\n平時買開股票<br />\n想問下有無年息3-5% bond推介<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小心賺息輸價<br />\n要留意派息有幾多%係由本金攞出來</blockquote><br />\n我對bond無乜認識<br />\n有無邊種bond係到期一定收到定額息而唔會影響到本金？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大把bond有monthly cash distribution<br />\n可以去 FSM 到望下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好多喺銀行 retail banking 賣嘅基金，佢都會話保證有幾多厘息，嗰啲九成九都係呃你，佢事實上係本金度攞返錢畀你<br />\n<br />\n譬如你畀$1,000去買fund A, 佢保證一年有10%息， 表面睇落去好吸引。 但係你一年之後就會發覺fund A ge價值得番$900 亦即係話佢根本上冇畀到利息你，只係巧立名目咁樣話你賺咗錢(入咗100蚊落去你Cash account)。 佢嗰啲利息會逐日逐日畀你，所以你唔會睇到突然間有一日會多左或者少咗錢。"},{"pid":"629372ac2126def2449bb5c1348554463e7f2c5f","tid":183651,"uid":40173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:21:14.000Z","msg":"加息買債咪玩啦，買股息穩定既仲好"},{"pid":"3db8707fd102de0e97e0354ce6e1fe358d200dbf","tid":183651,"uid":89478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:39:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同問<br />\n平時買開股票<br />\n想問下有無年息3-5% bond推介<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/no